Jointed lab meetings were taken place. Planning with them that making theses using material from OKEON project.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Subtropical Field Science Center at University of Ryukyus</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Helping establishment of the field sites at Oku, Yona, and two at the Campus in the Univ. of Ryukyus.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Ryukyu University Museum, Fujukan</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Giving us advices on the curatorial system, on site localities, and connecting to the Okinawan community of conservation biology.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Okinawa Prefectural Museum</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing us a cold space for storing specimens. Cooperation on their exhibition is planning.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Se-fa Utakim, the world heritage</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Kurashiki Dam</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Nago Central Park</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Nakagusuku Park</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site. Suggested us some connections in the Okinawan society.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Okinawa Prefectural Forest Park</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Heiwasozo-no-mori Park</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site</span>	\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Tamagusuku Youth and Children''s Center</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site, and they are willing the cooperation with us on development of an environmental education program.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Hentona High School</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site. Established an ant research team in their class program, and their research were selected in the 36th Exhibition of the Science-work by the students in Okinawa.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Kyuyo High School</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Established an ant research team in their class program, and their research were selected in the 36th Exhibition of the Science-work by the students in Okinawa. We found several undetermined ant species in their material.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Futenma High School</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Established an ant research team in their biology club program, and their research were selected in the 36th Exhibition of the Science-work by the students in Okinawa. We found an undetermined ant species in their material. It is the species, which is at least the first record in Japan.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Kaiho High School</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Established an ant research team in their class program, and their research were selected in the 36th Exhibition of the Science-work by the students in Okinawa.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Higashi Museum</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Helping us to get the permission to set up a site at the mangrove forest in Higashi son.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Community at the mangrove forest in Kesaji Gulf, National Heritage</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>They have accepted setting a site up at the mangrove forest area, and planning using the site for the local environmental education.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Bird Forest Nature Park, Uruma City</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Nago Museum</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site and helping us to get the permission to set up a site at the Mt. Katsu-dake in Nago City.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Onna-Son Museum</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Discussing the way to cooperation for the research on the natural history in the village.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Okinawa City Museum</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site, and cooperated on their exhibition, helped us to make multiple connections to Okinawan Society, planning cooperation on their new exhibition.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Chatan Town Hall</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site, gave us suggestions for setting soil sensors.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Sueyoshi Park (Naha City)</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site, helped us to find a site in Sueyoshi Park.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Mori-no-ie Minmin</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Helped us to find a site in Sueyoshi Park.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Yambaru Discovery Forest</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Southeast Botanical Gardens</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Ohyama Yam Farm</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Providing a site.</span>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>+ Mr. Takamine</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>Provided the reference collection of Okinawan ants.</span>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<h3> Publications </h3>\r\n<p> \r\n<span class = ''bold''>Yoshimura M, Yoshida T, Ogasawara M & Economo E (<em>in press</em>)</span> Ant Research Program for High School Students Using the Time-unit Sampling Method. Research Bulletin of Environmental Education Center,　Miyagi University of Education.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<h3> Media Release </h3>\r\n<p>\r\n<span class = ''bold''>Newspaper</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>2015 Nov 16 Ryukyu Shinpo</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>2015 Nov 28 Okinawa Times</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>2015 Dec 04 Ryukyu Shinpo</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>2016 Jan 29 Ryukyu Shinpo</span>\r\n\r\n<span class = ''bold''>TV</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>2015 Nov 26 RBC News</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>2015 Dec 16 RBC News</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>2016 Feb 28 TBS Bessatsu Asahi Journal</span>\r\n\r\n<span class = ''bold''>Radio</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>2015 Oct 15 Typhoon FM Hitowaku</span>\r\n<span class = ''padding-left-20''>2015 Nov 15 Typhoon FM Magical Mystery Tour</span>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n[:]', '[:en]Achievements[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '620-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-29 04:26:50', '2016-07-29 04:26:50', '', 620, 'http://localhost:8888/wp-okeon/htdocs/?p=638', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
